definitions.definition: Likely to follow or yield to physical pressure ; easily shaped or molded .
Likely to follow , conform , or yield to others, especially showing unthinking adherence to others' ideas; easily led.

labels: Of musical notes or poetic feet
definitions.label_groups: Of musical notes or poetic feet

definitions.definition: Following logically or in an unvarying and orderly procession , tending in a single intellectual direction .

main_definition: ( Of objects , obsolete ) Likely to follow or yield to physical pressure ; easily shaped or molded .
secondary_definitions: ( Of people ) Likely to follow , conform , or yield to others, especially showing unthinking adherence to others' ideas; easily led.
( Of musical notes or poetic feet ) Following neatly or smoothly .
( Of thought ) Following logically or in an unvarying and orderly procession , tending in a single intellectual direction .
